  <script async="" type="text/javascript">
   (async function() {
  
  const ADS_URL = 'https://paywall.production.ippen.space/js/dfp.min.js';
  const BANNER_DATAATTR_LOGIN_URL = "data-id-login-url";
  const BANNER_DATAATTR_REGISTER_URL = "data-id-register-url";
  const PRODUCT_ID = "0071";
  const AUTH_BASE_URL = "https://auth.production.ippen.space/oauth/authorize";
  const PORTAL_BASE_URL = "https://www.fr.de/";
  const CLIENT_ID = "fr";
  const CHECKOUT_URL = "https://checkout.ippen-digital.de/shop/be9eb4b5-cdb9-4437-a36c-d14de7dcf43f";
  
  function getCurrentUrl() {
    var parts = document.location.href.split('?');
    return parts.length >= 2 ? parts[0] : document.location.href;
  }

  function generateRandomString(len) {
    var text = "";
    var charset = "abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz0123456789";
    for (var i = 0; i < len; i++)
      text += charset.charAt(Math.floor(Math.random() * charset.length));
    return text;
  }
  
  function getLoginUrl() {
    var state = generateRandomString(10);
    var currentUrl = getCurrentUrl();
    return AUTH_BASE_URL + '?state=' + state + '&register=false&scope=openid&audience=' 
      + CLIENT_ID + '&response_type=code&client_id=' + CLIENT_ID + '&redirect_uri=' + PORTAL_BASE_URL 
      + '?redirect_uri%3D' + currentUrl;
  }

  function getRegisterUrl() {
    var state = generateRandomString(10);
    var converted = generateRandomString(5);
    var currentUrl = getCurrentUrl();
    return AUTH_BASE_URL + '?state=' + state + '&register=true&scope=openid&audience=' + CLIENT_ID 
    + '&response_type=code&client_id=' + CLIENT_ID + '&redirect_uri=' + PORTAL_BASE_URL 
    + '?redirect_uri%3D' + CHECKOUT_URL + '?origin%253D' + currentUrl + '%25253Fconverted%25253D' + converted;
  }
  
  function isArticle() {
    var articleElement = document.getElementsByClassName('id-Article');
    return articleElement != null && articleElement.length > 0;
  }

  function getCookie(name) {
    var value = "; " + document.cookie;
    var parts = value.split("; " + name + "=");
    return parts.length >= 2 ? parts.pop().split(";").shift() : '';
  }
 
  function hasAdFreeProduct() {
    var acl = getCookie('ACL');
    var uuid = getCookie('UUID');
    return uuid && acl && acl.includes(PRODUCT_ID);
  }
 
  function getAndIncrementPagesViewed() {
    var pageViews = getCookie('ad_free_page_views');
 
    if (pageViews && pageViews != null) {
      pageViews = Number(pageViews) + 1;
    } else {
      pageViews = 1;
    }
     
    document.cookie = 'ad_free_page_views=' + pageViews + ';max-age=' + (3600*24);
 
    return pageViews;
  }
  
  async function hasAdBlocker() {
    var isBlocked;

    async function callAdsUrl() {
      try {
        return fetch(
          new Request(ADS_URL, {
            method: 'GET',
            mode: 'no-cors'
          }))
          .then(function(response) {
            isBlocked = false;
            return isBlocked;
          }).catch(function(e) {
            isBlocked = true;
            return isBlocked;
          });
      } catch (error) {
        isBlocked = false;
        return isBlocked;
      }
    }

     return isBlocked !== undefined ? isBlocked : await callAdsUrl();
   }
  
  async function checkShowAdBlockBanner() {
    var freePageviewsLimit = 1;
    var isAdBlocker = await hasAdBlocker();    

    if (isArticle() && isAdBlocker && !hasAdFreeProduct()) {
      var pagesViewed = getAndIncrementPagesViewed();
 
      if (pagesViewed > freePageviewsLimit) {
        var banner = document.getElementById('id-wf-abo');
        if (banner) {
           banner.style.display = "flex";
           banner.setAttribute(BANNER_DATAATTR_LOGIN_URL, getLoginUrl());
           banner.setAttribute(BANNER_DATAATTR_REGISTER_URL, getRegisterUrl());
           document.body.style.overflowY = 'hidden';
           dataLayer.push({'event': 'page_view_fr_puroverlay'});
        }
      }
    }
  }
   
  if (document.readyState === 'loading') {
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', checkShowAdBlockBanner);
  } else {
    checkShowAdBlockBanner();
  }

})();
  </script>
